title: this looks like it should error instead
pid: 9dae7e53-70cf-496f-9c29-f2c9b42b9622
body: |2-
  let (pid_resolved, source) : (ID, SourceName) =
    // Query TypeDB for PID and source
    ( match pid_and_source_from_id(
      &config.db_name, driver, &pid).await?
      { Some(result) => result,
        None => { // No such node in database. Return input unchanged.
          return Ok(from_user); }} );
